WEBVTT

00:00:27.192 --> 00:00:30.312
gacha faylasuflar, psixologlar, 
mutafakkirlar,

00:00:30.312 --> 00:00:34.514
olimlar, rassomlar, 
dinshunoslar va siyosatchilar

00:00:34.514 --> 00:00:38.433
mavjudlik tushunchasini 
tushunishga harakat qildi.

00:00:38.433 --> 00:00:42.990
Ular turli farazlarni ilgari surdilar, 
ammo hech qanday kelishuvga erishmadilar.

00:00:42.990 --> 00:00:44.600
Ushbu savol ustida aqlli odamlar

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:49.540
bosh qotirdilar, lekin nega 
unga javob topish juda qiyin?

00:00:49.540 --> 00:00:51.559
Birinchi qiyinchilik - bu

00:00:51.559 --> 00:00:56.301
tushunchaning murakkab tabiati
"Shaxsning doimiyligi."

00:00:56.301 --> 00:00:58.490
O'zingizdagi "Men" aslida "Kim?"

00:00:58.490 --> 00:01:00.095
Bugun siz kimsiz? Yoki